com.digev.mp.pipeline

Interface IWSInfo

  • Deprecated. 
    Please see Message.

    public interface IWSInfo
    The WSInfo interface defines the message context used to store all information related to processing a message in the Management Point. Instances of this interface are passed to all pipoeline (policy) components during both request and response processing.
